====================================
1. Prerequisites
====================================
------------------
1.1 Dependencies
------------------
*. FBX SDK for VS2008
*. GLUT and GLEW

a. http://usa.autodesk.com/adsk/servlet/index?siteID=123112&id=7478532
b. see the folder ./GL, ./glutx86, ./glutx64

====================================
2. Usage
====================================
Render FBX files into scene, and obtain the depth map and label in certain ROI.

An command line file should also be provided.

